  <div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>National Sleep Research Resource</h1>
    <p class="lead">Explore the largest collection of sleep research databases in the world.</p>
    <p>
      <%= link_to 'Get started today', 'https://sleepepi.partners.org/slice/survey/nsrr-sleepdata', target: '_blank', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-success' %>
    </p>
  </div>

    <div class="marketing">

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <%= image_tag 'shhs_logo.png', size: '140x140', alt: 'SHHS' %>
          <h2>Sleep Heart Health Study</h2>
          <p>Download and explore the dataset that started it all. The quintessential SHHS dataset follows the sleep patterns of 6,000 individuals over three visits.</p>
          <p>
            <%= link_to 'View details &raquo;'.html_safe, '#', data: { object: 'suppress-click' }, class: 'btn btn-default' %>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <%= image_tag 'chat_logo.png', size: '140x140', alt: 'SHHS' %>
          <h2>CHAT</h2>
          <p>The most comprehensive dataset of children with sleep apnea. Leading sleep researchers in the field regard the Childhood Adenotonsillectomy Study as the gold standard for understanding sleep apnea present in children.</p>
          <p>
            <%= link_to 'View details &raquo;'.html_safe, '#', data: { object: 'suppress-click' }, class: 'btn btn-default' %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <%= image_tag 'bestair_logo.png', size: '140x140', alt: 'SHHS' %>
          <h2>BestAIR</h2>
          <p>Cutting edge data and results will soon be available on www.sleepdata.org from the BestAIR study. Novel device setups, montage tweaks, and immaculate manuals of procedures are included in this dataset.</p>
          <p>
            <%= link_to 'View details &raquo;'.html_safe, '#', data: { object: 'suppress-click' }, class: 'btn btn-default' %>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="soften">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Download the data. <span class="text-muted">For free.</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">And remember to cite the National Sleep Research Resource in your next paper or presentation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <%= image_tag 'charts.png', size: '500x500', alt: 'Charts', class: 'featurette-image img-responsive' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="soften">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <%= image_tag 'reports.png', size: '500x500', alt: 'Reports', class: 'featurette-image img-responsive' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Share your findings. <span class="text-muted">See for yourself.</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">With an intuitive web interface, you will not require fancy SAS coding knowledge to generate reports that will wow your colleauges.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="soften">

      <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Follow the data. <span class="text-muted">Stay ahead of the curve. </span></h2>
          <p class="lead">Track the progress of your favorite datasets, and get notified when they are updated.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <%= image_tag 'track.png', size: '500x500', alt: 'Track', class: 'featurette-image img-responsive' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="soften">

